songs.title: White Hoes
songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
I'm in a ghost, with some white hoes
And the cufs start to hurt (Skrrt, skrrt, skrrt, skrrt)
Hunnid band lean today, my bitch she wit’ okay (Ooh)
Was jugging for hoes, I pour a four
I'm feeling like shit today (Lean)
VVS chain on me, she brought racks to me
I'm in a ghost, with some white hoes
And they be cuffing me

[Verse]
And my whole wardrobe designer cause I’m geeking (Bands)
